            </p>
            <div class="hero-download-buttons">
                <a href="#" class="app-store-button" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                    <img src="/assets/images/download-ios.png" alt="Download on the App Store" class="app-store-badge" />
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="google-play-button" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                    <img src="/assets/images/download-google.png" alt="Get it on Google Play" class="google-play-badge" />
                </a>
            </div>
            <p class="hero-legal">
                Al descargar la aplicación, aceptas 
                los <a href="/terminos">Términos del servicio</a> y la <a href="/privacidad">Política de privacidad</a>.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-image">
            <div class="phone-preview">
                <img src="/assets/images/hero-iphone~dark-6KYLSRYT.png" alt="El Estoico App Preview" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain; border-radius: 2rem;" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
